channel.title: It wont let me logon!
channel.description: When I press login this is what it says on my runserver: [code]Starting SanitationScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 ClientHandler: Accepted from MY NAME:2044 Client type: high memory version UserId: 19053999 X Pk X has signed onto server. [/code] But it never logs me in... Then it says error connectiing to server, then it says my account is already logged in.
